Description_Lang_enUS: An organization focused on protecting Azeroth from the threat of the Scourge.  Strongholds of the Argent Dawn can be found in the Eastern and Western Plaguelands.
Voren'thal the Seer leads the dissident blood elves who've rejected Kael'thas' path to power.  They've joined forces with the naaru of Shattrath City, much to the dismay of the Aldor.
The Centaur Clan who seek peace and unification through the efforts of the nomadic tribes.

Description_Lang_enUS: The Centaur Clan driven by aggression, seeking to conquer the Desolace wastes and crush all opposition.
